Class LineageMasterClientServiceHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • tachyon.master.lineage.LineageMasterClientServiceHandler

    LineageMasterClientService.Iface, TachyonService.Iface

    public final class LineageMasterClientServiceHandler
extends Object
implements LineageMasterClientService.Iface
    This class is a Thrift handler for lineage master RPCs invoked by a Tachyon client.
